name: Sentry
description:
A Black-Capped Chickadee perches among the branches of a Juniper tree to keep a watchful eye for predators while its banditry kin forage for food on a sunny winter day.

2017. Nikon D60, 55-200mm Lens.

Photographed in situ, without the use of artificial lighting or staging. Photoshop only used for resizing.

Birb Series: Part 1 - Chickadee IV
